@TOPublicHealth @cityoftoronto Friendly reminder that the 2nd round of Pfizer docs that the FDA wanted sealed until 2097 are being released tomorrow March 1 2022. 

Pay attention.

@TOPublicHealth You people are monsters. I have lost count of how many "sudden" deaths and injuries post jabs I have heard of. Another heart attack this morning - recently "triple jabbed"  This is genocide. https://t.co/pq8QgnpOcc

2/2: Thank you, TO for continuing to do your part to help stop #COVID19 spread & keep our community safe. If you haven't already, there are many opportunities to get your 1st, 2nd, 3rd or children's doses of the #COVID19 vaccine. Find a clinic near you: https://t.co/WlNW4JvkM0
